summary: USA & CANADA: David Tennant stars as Walt in Camping which premieres on HBO at 10pm ET/PT tonight. The cast also includes...
caption:
USA & CANADA: David Tennant stars as Walt in Camping which premieres on HBO at 10pm ET/PT tonight. The cast also includes Jennifer Garner as Walt’s controlling wife Kathryn.

Episode #1: Pilot
Written by Lena Dunham & Jenni Konner; directed by Jenni Konner.
A “perfect” group camping trip, obsessively organized by Kathryn McSorley-Jodell (Jennifer Garner) in honour of her adoring husband Walt’s (David Tennant) 45th birthday, is threatened by tension between Kathryn and her estranged best friend, Nina-Joy (Janicza Bravo), the unexpected addition of a pissed-off goth teen (Cheyenne Haynes) and the chaotic arrival of Miguel (Arturo Del Puerto), who is smack dab in the middle of a breakdown and toting his new girlfriend, Jandice (Juliette Lewis), a woman of many talents who rubs Kathryn the wrong way.

summary: I just rewatched the Ballad of Russell and Julie that David Tennant, John Barrowman, and Catherine Tate did for Russell T....
body: I just rewatched the Ballad of Russell and Julie that David Tennant, John Barrowman, and Catherine Tate did for Russell T. Davies and Julie Gardner when they were departing as showrunner and exec. producer, and I love it so much still but now I’m wondering why something like that wasn’t done for Steven Moffat. I mean, Russell and Julie were responsible for rebooting Doctor Who in 2005 so it was a huge deal and they deserved that hilarious and awesome video, but still… someone could’ve done a lil something for Steven. Like maybe Matt, Karen, Arthur could’ve returned and in conjunction with perhaps Jenna, Peter, Pearl, Michelle could’ve done a thing, a song, a video similar to what David, John, and Catherine did. Well anyway, it doesn’t matter, just thoughts.

summary: AUDIO: David Tennant & Catherine Tate Interviewed For Big Finish Podcast
title: AUDIO: David Tennant & Catherine Tate Interviewed For Big Finish Podcast
excerpt: David Tennant and Catherine Tate feature in the latest edition of the Big Finish podcast, now available to stream or download. The pair ...
description:
David Tennant and Catherine Tate feature in the latest edition of the Big Finish podcast, now available to stream or download. The pair took part in an interview during their recent visit to the Big Finish studios to record a new series of Tenth Doctor audio adventures for release next year.

The weekly round up of Big Finish’s world of audiobooks and audio drama is hosted by Nick Briggs and Benji Clifford. You can download the podcast here or listen below. David and Catherine appear from about 34m:30s in; also included is the first 15 minutes of Torchwood: God Among Us - Future Pain starring John Barrowman and Tracy-Ann Oberman.
